# Root Ocean / Pure Water  
Universal Institutional Submission Repository

## Overview
This repository contains the complete universal submission pack for the Root Ocean / Pure Water project.  
It is designed for global institutions, research bodies, development partners, and humanitarian organizations seeking clear, neutral, and collaborative information on water safety and environmental resilience.

All documents are:
- Informational  
- Non‑jurisdictional  
- Non‑binding  
- Globally readable  
- Professionally structured  
- Safe for institutional review  

No legal authority is claimed.  
No enforcement language is used.

